00:40:27,657 --> 00:40:30,557
けど、けど、けど...
But, but, but...

637
00:40:32,557 --> 00:40:36,357
三角形 三角形の恋は気まぐれ
Triangle, triangle love is whimsical

638
00:40:37,857 --> 00:40:41,757
一瞬で 一瞬で崩れるバランス
In an instant, in an instant, the balance collapses

639
00:40:43,857 --> 00:40:47,357
普通の恋 夢みてたのに
Even though I dreamed of a normal love...

640
00:40:48,857 --> 00:40:50,357
ノーマル設定の私じゃ
...for the "normal" setting me...

641
00:40:50,457 --> 00:40:53,057
ちょっと無理ゲーすぎます
...it's just a bit too much of an unbeatable game

642
00:40:54,557 --> 00:40:58,357
三角形 三角形の恋は不安定
Triangle, triangle love is unstable

643
00:40:59,857 --> 00:41:03,857
なんちゃって なんちゃってじゃ済まないカテゴリー
Just kidding, just kidding won't suffice for this category

644
00:41:05,857 --> 00:41:09,357
彼女のこと 好きになれたらな
If I could just fall in love with her...

645
00:41:10,857 --> 00:41:14,357
なんて妄想しちゃいます
...that's the kind of delusion I'm having

646
00:41:15,857 --> 00:41:19,357
私 どうかしてます
Something's wrong with me

647
00:41:21,857 --> 00:41:23,057
行くよー！
Here we go!

648
00:41:48,857 --> 00:41:51,057
Wow! Awesome!

649
00:41:51,157 --> 00:41:53,557
Oh my god, it's so much fun! Wow!

650
00:41:53,657 --> 00:41:56,057
Happy birthday FuwaMoco!

651
00:41:58,557 --> 00:42:01,057
You look not looking very silly at all, Mococo!
You don't look silly at all, Mococo!

652
00:42:03,257 --> 00:42:05,057
Miko-senpai! Wow! Hi!

653
00:42:06,557 --> 00:42:10,057
I think I need to get out of here!

654
00:42:20,057 --> 00:42:21,557
バウバウ！
Bau bau!

655
00:42:22,557 --> 00:42:23,857
