665
00:42:50,557 --> 00:42:52,557
...and Triangle Dreamer!

666
00:42:53,057 --> 00:42:56,057
With Miko-senpai, Mio-senpai, and Subaru-senpai!

667
00:42:56,557 --> 00:42:58,557
What'd you think, Ruffians?

668
00:42:59,557 --> 00:43:02,057
Now Kiss Me, I Stayed Together, it's a song that...

669
00:43:02,257 --> 00:43:05,557
...I've always wanted to sing together with Ah-kun!

670
00:43:06,057 --> 00:43:09,557
Yeah, it's a little bit more sexy... a bit sexy song, huh? Yeah.

671
00:43:10,557 --> 00:43:12,057
And Triangle Dreamer!

672
00:43:12,557 --> 00:43:14,557
Yeah! The bestest idol song!

673
00:43:15,057 --> 00:43:18,057
Yeah, so the Yuri development was too cute...

674
00:43:18,557 --> 00:43:20,057
Ruffians... are you still alive?

675
00:43:20,557 --> 00:43:22,057
Are you alive?

676
00:43:22,557 --> 00:43:26,557
Yeah! All senpai were so cute in love.

677
00:43:28,557 --> 00:43:31,057
Yeah, and then crowd surfing on the bubble!

678
00:43:31,557 --> 00:43:33,057
Whoa!

679
00:43:34,557 --> 00:43:38,557
