大きめサイズの、可愛いアイドルのフワモコアクリルスタンド！
Large-sized, cute idol FuwaMoco acrylic stands!

696
00:44:31,057 --> 00:44:33,257
Next, we have the silly Ehehe Angel...

697
00:44:33,557 --> 00:44:36,057
