704
00:44:58,557 --> 00:45:02,057
We'll be the same size as our Friends with U plushies, so you can display them together!

705
00:45:02,472 --> 00:45:05,272
おしゃべりパッピーMOCOCOぬいぐるみのふわもこだよ！
I'm the Talking Puppy MOCOCO Plushie, Fuwamoco!

706
00:45:05,272 --> 00:45:08,272
ぎゅっとすると色々と喋るよ！
