707
00:45:08,272 --> 00:45:11,172
どんなボイスが出るかお楽しみに！
Look forward to hearing what voices I have!

708
00:45:11,172 --> 00:45:14,772
We have the Fuwawa and Mococo to GO☆ Finger Puppets!

709
00:45:14,772 --> 00:45:21,872
They both come with one extra Ruffians kigurumi costume
