710
00:45:21,872 --> 00:45:24,272
FUWAWAとMOCOCOの指パペット！
FUWAWA and MOCOCO Finger Puppets!

711
00:45:24,272 --> 00:45:28,972
どこでも一緒に連れていけるサイズで、
着せ替えラフィアンズ衣装もあるよ！
They're a size you can take anywhere,
and they come with a Ruffians costume!

712
00:45:28,972 --> 00:45:35,672
Finally, we have two different ASMR voice packs:
"Back from a Fluffy Date♡" from Fuwawa...

713
00:45:35,672 --> 00:45:39,272
...and "Sweet and Fuzzy Needy Puppy" from Mococo.

714
00:45:39,272 --> 00:45:43,972
ASMRボイスは、英語と日本語、
両方で収録してます！
The ASMR voices are recorded in
both English and Japanese!

715
