722
00:46:20,472 --> 00:46:24,972
We put lots of love into each and every signature,
so we hope you look forward to it!

723
00:46:24,972 --> 00:46:27,972
たくさんの愛情を込めて、サイン書きますね！
I'll write the signatures with lots of love!

724
00:46:27,972 --> 00:46:33,672
Please check out the hololive Official Online Shop and
look for the link in the description or comment area, okay?

725
00:46:33,672 --> 00:46:37,772
ぜひ、ホロライブ公式ショップを
チェックしてください！
Please be sure to check out the
hololive Official Shop!

726
00:46:37,772 --> 00:46:38,972
Bau bau!

727
00:46:38,972 --> 00:46:40,672
What did you think, Ruffians?

728
00:46:40,672 --> 00:46:43,672
Of our birthday merch! Pretty cute, huh?

729
00:46:43,672 --> 00:46:44,572
Yeah!

730
00:46:44,572 --> 00:46:47,772
The reservations will be going on sale right

731
00:46:47,772 --> 00:46:51,272
after the birthday live here ends, so don't forget, okay?

732
00:46:51,272 --> 00:46:55,472
生誕のグッズの予約は、この後開始しますので、
Pre-orders for the birthday merch will start after this,

733
00:46:55,472 --> 00:46:59,272
お忘れなくチェックしてください！
so please don't forget to check it out!

734
00:46:59,272 --> 00:47:02,472
You can find the link below or on the side here!

735
00:47:02,472 --> 00:47:05,472
Don't forget, okay? Bau bau!

736
00:47:05,472 --> 00:47:10,472
We put a lot of love into it, and Icomochi-mama too!

737
00:47:10,472 --> 00:47:13,472
Time to go, go, go! Go buy it!

738
00:47:13,472 --> 00:47:15,472
Well, we performed

739
00:47:15,472 --> 00:47:20,472
another special collab song with our dear senpai!

740
00:47:20,472 --> 00:47:24,972
But there's still one mystery guest we haven't met yet, right?

741
00:47:24,972 --> 00:47:28,972
まだ会ってない、謎のゲストが一人いるんだよ！
There's one mystery guest we haven't met yet!

742
00:47:28,972 --> 00:47:32,472
Well, should we give the Ruffians a hint?

743
00:47:32,472 --> 00:47:35,672
Ruffians, who could it be?

744
00:47:35,672 --> 00:47:36,972
Hokuro P?

745
00:47:36,972 --> 00:47:38,272
YAGOO-san?

746
00:47:38,272 --> 00:47:41,472
Ah, YAGOO-san! That's a good guess maybe, but...

747
00:47:41,472 --> 00:47:45,472
Well, you should get ready, because...

748
00:47:45,472 --> 00:47:49,972
You know, they aren't quite as bad as Pero,

749
00:47:49,972 --> 00:47:54,472
but they can get pretty nasty sometimes!

750
00:47:54,472 --> 00:47:57,972
Mococo-chan, you're not going to be rude to our next guest

751
00:47:57,972 --> 00:48:02,472
or anything, right? Especially before calling them out!

752
00:48:02,472 --> 00:48:04,972
We'll see!

753
00:48:04,972 --> 00:48:07,972
Well, let's get them out here then!

754
00:48:07,972 --> 00:48:11,772
Who could it be? Okay, se-no... douzo!
Who could it be? Okay, one, two... come on out!

755
00:48:11,772 --> 00:48:15,972
わわわわ！きたしんや！きたしんや！
Wa wa wa wa! I've arrived-shin! I've arrived-shin!

756
00:48:15,972 --> 00:48:19,272
きたしんや！
I've arrived-shin!

757
00:48:19,272 --> 00:48:23,472
ポポンちゅー！
Popon-chu!

758
00:48:23,472 --> 00:48:25,972
自己紹介お願いします！
Please introduce yourself!

759
00:48:25,972 --> 00:48:31,472
クロちゃんです！わわわわー！
I'm Kuro-chan! Wa wa wa wa!

760
00:48:31,472 --> 00:48:34,472
はじめまして！
Nice to meet you!

761
00:48:34,472 --> 00:48:36,972
チワワじゃないよ！ふわわだよ！
I'm not a Chihuahua! I'm Fuwawa!

762
00:48:36,972 --> 00:48:39,472
ふわわじゃないよ！もここだよ！
I'm not Fuwawa! I'm Mococo!

763
00:48:39,472 --> 00:48:42,472
二人合わせて、ふわもこです！
Together, we are FuwaMoco!

764
00:48:42,472 --> 00:48:48,972
バウバウ！よろしくお願いします！
Bau bau! Nice to meet you!

765
00:48:48,972 --> 00:48:53,472
ふわもこのわちゃわちゃバースデーフェスティバルに
来てくれてありがとうございます！
Thank you for coming to FuwaMoco's
Wacha Wacha Birthday Festival!

766
00:48:53,472 --> 00:48:57,472
ハッピーバースデーだしんよ！ふわもこ！
Happy Birthday-shin! FuwaMoco!

767
00:48:57,472 --> 00:49:00,672
いいしんねー！
It's great-shin!

768
00:49:00,672 --> 00:49:04,972
ちょっとね、視聴者のラフィアンズは
たくさんいると思いますけど、
I'm sure there are many Ruffians watching,

769
00:49:04,972 --> 00:49:10,272
クロちゃんがどんな人なのか説明してもらえますか？
could you explain what kind of person Kuro-chan is?

770
00:49:10,272 --> 00:49:13,472
自分でんの？それ？ introduction!
I have to do it myself? Okay, introduction!

771
00:49:13,472 --> 00:49:17,972
わかったしんよ。だってこれ海外の人も見てますもんね。
Got it-shin. People from overseas are watching too, right?

772
00:49:17,972 --> 00:49:20,472
海外の人もわかる自己紹介しますからね。
I'll do a self-introduction that overseas people can understand.

773
00:49:20,472 --> 00:49:25,972
Nice to meet you, nice to meet you, chu, chu, chu, chu, Tulip!

774
00:49:25,972 --> 00:49:29,972
え、困らないで。クロちゃんはチューリップ？
Wait, don't look puzzled. Kuro-chan is a tulip?

775
00:49:29,972 --> 00:49:33,472
チューリップ？ No no no!
Tulip? No no no!

776
00:49:33,472 --> 00:49:38,472
え、ちょっとまだ分からないかもしれないから。
Maybe they don't understand yet.

777
00:49:38,472 --> 00:49:43,472
えーとに、安田大サーカスというトリオを組んでる芸人さんで、
Well, I'm a comedian in a trio called Yasuda Dai Circus,

778
00:49:43,472 --> 00:49:46,972
あと豆柴の大群のプロデューサーもやってまして、
and I'm also the producer for Mameshiba no Taigun,

779
00:49:46,972 --> 00:49:49,972
作詞とかもしています、クロちゃんです！バウバウ！
and I write lyrics too. I'm Kuro-chan! Bau bau!

780
00:49:49,972 --> 00:49:53,472
じゃあ今度は英語でお願いします！ In English!
Now do it in English! In English!

781
00:49:53,472 --> 00:49:55,472
僕が？自分で？
Me? By myself?

782
00:49:55,472 --> 00:49:58,972
え、そんなこと急に言われたら… It's Shine! Flower!
If you ask me so suddenly... It's Shine! Flower!

783
00:49:58,972 --> 00:50:02,472
No no no!

784
00:50:02,081 --> 00:50:03,748
言い訳はなし！
No excuses!

785
00:50:03,881 --> 00:50:06,048
聞いてる？人の話！
Are you listening? To what I'm saying!

786
00:50:06,181 --> 00:50:07,081
頑張って！
Good luck!

787
00:50:07,281 --> 00:50:09,348
えっと、なんだろう... えっと...
Uh, what should I say... Uh...

788
00:50:10,481 --> 00:50:11,848
Famous Comedian!

789
00:50:13,681 --> 00:50:15,448
Idol Producer!

790
00:50:17,281 --> 00:50:18,748
やってるしんよ！
He's actually doing it!

791
00:50:19,281 --> 00:50:20,448
できるしんよ！
He can do it!

792
00:50:21,381 --> 00:50:23,748
クロちゃんテレビでよく見てるけど...
We often see Kuro-chan on TV, but...

793
00:50:24,281 --> 00:50:29,648
ちょっとフワモコのペットのペロちゃんと、えっと、ちょっと似てるところがたくさんあるね！
There are a lot of similarities to FuwaMoco's pet, Pero-chan!

794
00:50:31,181 --> 00:50:34,348
ちょっと後ろの飾り見てください！見えますか？
Please look at the decorations behind us! Can you see them?

795
00:50:36,181 --> 00:50:37,948
そっくりでペロです！ペロ！
He's a spitting image of Pero! Pero!

796
00:50:38,481 --> 00:50:41,048
ちょっと待って！球体というか、丸いところが似てるだけじゃない？
Wait a minute! Isn't it just that he's spherical, or round, that's similar?

797
00:50:41,981 --> 00:50:43,248
そうじゃない！
That's not it!

798
00:50:43,481 --> 00:50:44,248
本当？
Really?

799
00:50:45,281 --> 00:50:51,648
えっとクロちゃんと似てるところは、嘘つきで、女の子好きで、やらしい... うん！
The similarities to Kuro-chan are: a liar, a lady-killer, and lecherous... yep!

800
00:50:52,381 --> 00:50:56,548
だからね、見た目で騙されないで！クロちゃんはそれで大丈夫なの？言われて...
So, don't be fooled by appearances! Is it okay for Kuro-chan to be told that?

801
00:50:57,381 --> 00:51:01,248
いや、ひどい！悲しくなってきた！え〜ん、え〜ん、え〜ん！
No, that's mean! I'm getting sad! Waaah, waaah, waaah!

802
00:51:01,581 --> 00:51:04,048
エンポコエンフン！
En-po-ko-en-fu!

803
00:51:05,181 --> 00:51:07,948
全然人のギャグを聞かないよね、君たちは！
You guys really don't listen to other people's gags!

804
00:51:09,381 --> 00:51:14,348
できればクロちゃんはペロの友達になってくれませんか？
If possible, won't you become Pero's friend, Kuro-chan?

805
00:51:15,381 --> 00:51:17,848
フワモコの友達じゃなくて、ペロの友達になるの？
Not FuwaMoco's friend, but Pero's friend?

806
00:51:18,381 --> 00:51:21,348
フワモコはクロちゃんと友達になりたくないから！
Because FuwaMoco doesn't want to be friends with Kuro-chan!

807
00:51:22,081 --> 00:51:23,148
おかしくない、それ？
Isn't that strange?

808
00:51:23,481 --> 00:51:25,048
いやいや、気持ち悪いから！
No, no, because it's gross!

809
00:51:25,681 --> 00:51:27,348
気持ち悪くない！マニアには受ける！
It's not gross! Enthusiasts will love it!

810
00:51:27,781 --> 00:51:30,348
違う！フワモコ気持ち悪いやっぱり！
No! FuwaMoco thinks it's gross after all!

811
00:51:31,381 --> 00:51:35,248
でもモコちゃん、ちょっとやりすぎですよ、失礼です！
But Mococo-chan, that's a bit too much, it's rude!

812
00:51:36,381 --> 00:51:42,348
いや、もしもしペロと仲良くなってほしいんだったら、フワモコちゃん、クロちゃんに可愛く頼んだほうがいいんじゃない？
Well, if you want me to get along with Pero, shouldn't FuwaMoco-chan ask Kuro-chan cutely?

813
00:51:43,181 --> 00:51:44,348
はぁ？ NO！
Hah? NO!

814
00:51:46,181 --> 00:51:47,248
えっ、NO？
Eh, NO?

815
00:51:47,381 --> 00:51:48,248
NO！
NO!

816
00:51:47,381 --> 00:51:48,748
しっかりとした否定！
A firm rejection!

817
00:51:49,281 --> 00:51:50,248
NO！
NO!

818
